eSSD</li><li>2TB Bandwidth</li><li>1000 Mbit/s Port</li><li>1 Usable IP Address</li><li>Istanbul Equinix IL2</li><li>Linux or Windows OS</li><li>$28.73/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://clients.hostigger.com/index.php?cmd=module&amp;module=77&amp;cid=334\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ORDER NOW</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>VMware Plan 3</b></p><ul><li>1 Core CPU</li><li>4GB RAM</li><li>40GB PureSSD</li><li>4TB Bandwidth</li><li>1000 Mbit/s Port</li><li>1 Usable IP Address</li><li>Istanbul Equinix IL2</li><li>Linux or Windows OS</li><li>$35.93/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://clients.hostigger.com/index.php?cmd=module&amp;module=77&amp;cid=335\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ORDER NOW</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>VMware Plan 4</b></p><ul><li>2 Core CPU</li><li>4GB RAM</li><li>50GB PureSSD</li><li>4TB Bandwidth</li><li>1000 Mbit/s Port</li><li>1 Usable IP Address</li><li>Istanbul Equinix IL2</li><li>Linux or Windows OS</li><li>$43.13/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://clients.hostigger.com/index.php?cmd=module&amp;module=77&amp;cid=336\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ORDER NOW</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>VMware Plan 5</b></p><ul><li>2 Core CPU</li><li>5GB RAM</li><li>50GB PureSSD</li><li>4TB Bandwidth</li><li>1000 Mbit/s Port</li><li>1 Usable IP Address</li><li>Istanbul Equinix IL2</li><li>Linux or Windows OS</li><li>$50.33/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://clients.hostigger.com/index.php?cmd=module&amp;module=77&amp;cid=337\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ORDER NOW</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Read more to see their node stats and network information.</p><p>And remember, leave your comments below.</p><p><span id=\"more-22338\"></span></p><div><p><strong>Network Information:</strong></p><div><p><strong>Istanbul